requirements?
Are we reporting our positions accurately?
Does my mark-to-market process accurately reflect the value of my
positions?
Are deals being entered properly and timely?
What is our confirmation process?
How will I know if our traders are trading within their limits?
How are position and credit limits established?
What is our exposure with counter-parties?

